---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Rogelio Gracia Otalvaro | Teaching & Education"
  description="Courses I teach and have taught at Embry-Riddle, plus my degrees from ICAI Comillas and ERAU."
>
<div class="sub has-bg">
  <div class="section__bg section__bg--flip" data-align="right" aria-hidden="true">
    <canvas data-dynamics="henon" data-direction="rtl" data-duration="2800" data-density="1.0" data-color="#5EC8FF"></canvas>
  </div>
  <a href="/" class="sub__back">&larr; Home</a>
  <h1 class="sub__title">Teaching & Education</h1>
  <div class="dyn-tag" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dyn-tag__kicker">Behind the text</span><span class="dyn-tag__name">Hénon attractor</span><span class="dyn-tag__sub">a strange attractor in two dimensions</span></div>
  <p class="sub__intro">Three courses this semester as a Visiting Assistant Professor. Before that, four years as a GTA building courses from scratch and teaching everything from circuit theory to nonlinear dynamics.</p>

  <h2>As Visiting Assistant Professor (Spring 2026)</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">CEC 315: Signals and Systems</div>
          <div class="card__org">Instructor &middot; 50 students</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Spring 2026</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Mathematical foundations for analyzing linear time-invariant systems: convolution, stability, Fourier series, Fourier and Laplace transforms, network analysis in the complex frequency domain.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">SYS 303: Optimization in Systems Engineering</div>
          <div class="card__org">Instructor &middot; 7 students</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Spring 2026</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Deterministic modeling, linear programming, duality, sensitivity analysis, integer and dynamic programming, network models, nonlinear programming.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">EE 620: Digital Communications</div>
          <div class="card__org">Instructor &middot; 7 students</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Spring 2026</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Digital communication theory: base-band and pass-band signal representations, matched filter, optimal detection, bit error rate analysis.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>As Graduate Teaching Assistant (2021-2025)</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">EE 327: Electrical Engineering Fundamentals</div>
          <div class="card__org">Instructor &middot; 90+ students (2 sections)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Fall 2025</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Circuit theory, AC/DC analysis, phasors, transient response, and digital logic.</p>
      <div class="tags">
        <span class="tag" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#166534;border-color:#bbf7d0">3.86/4.0 teaching effectiveness (College avg: 3.26)</span>
        <span class="tag" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#166534;border-color:#bbf7d0">89% "Strongly Agree" on effectiveness</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">SYS 699: Complex System Modeling</div>
          <div class="card__org">Content Designer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Summer 2023</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Original graduate course on system dynamics and agent-based modeling.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">EE 402: Control Systems Laboratory</div>
          <div class="card__org">Instructor</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Spring 2023</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">System identification, state feedback, controller implementation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">EE 401: Control Systems Analysis and Design</div>
          <div class="card__org">Teaching Assistant</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Spring 2023</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">ME 595FF: Dynamic Systems, Stability, and Control</div>
          <div class="card__org">Content Designer & TA</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Fall 2021 & Spring 2022</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">ES 204: Dynamics</div>
          <div class="card__org">Teaching Assistant</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">Fall 2021</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Education</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">Ph.D. in Computer Science & Electrical Engineering</div>
          <div class="card__org">Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University &middot; Daytona Beach, FL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">2023 &ndash; Dec 2025<br><span class="card__amount">GPA 4.0/4.0</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">M.S. in Mechanical Engineering</div>
          <div class="card__org">Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University &middot; Daytona Beach, FL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">2021 &ndash; 2022<br><span class="card__amount">GPA 3.83/4.0</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">M.S. in Industrial Technologies Engineering</div>
          <div class="card__org">ICAI Universidad Pontificia de Comillas &middot; Madrid, Spain</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">2020 &ndash; 2022<br><span class="card__amount">Thesis: 9.5/10</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">B.S. in Industrial Technologies Engineering</div>
          <div class="card__org">ICAI Universidad Pontificia de Comillas &middot; Madrid, Spain</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta">2015 &ndash; 2020<br><span class="card__amount">Thesis: 9.5/10</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
